profile:
Our services offer 35years of Carpentry Skills to assist you with all your various home projects from small necessary repairs to upgrade renovations, to edits and changes required to age in place with ease. 
We offer services and assistance when no handy hands are available due to health restrictions, limited physical ability, lack of time, skills and/or interest.
